      "text": "Play my favourite music\n\nControl temperature and humidity in room\n\nControl lights, blinds, etc.\n\nWatch movies, games, shows on tv\n\nBook tennis, yoga, etc.\n\nSet alarm clock\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
